text: The SNCF Class BB 16100 electric locomotives were converted from class BB 16000s by fitting TDM push-pull equipment to work the Paris Nord to St. Quentin/Amiens services as well as Paris St Lazare - Rouen. ==Conversions== * 16101 from 16004 * 16102 from 16017 * 16103 from 16046 * 16104 from 16040 * 16105 from 16014 * 16106 from 16009 * 16107 from 16048 * 16108 from 16026 * 16109 from 16023 * 16110 from 16035 * 16111 from 16016 * 16112 from 16010 * 16113 from 16030 * 16114 from 16062 * 16115 from 16060 ==References== Category:MTE locomotives Category:Bo′Bo′ locomotives 16100 Category:Railway locomotives introduced in 1991 Category:25 kV AC locomotives Category:Standard gauge electric locomotives of France
title: SNCF Class BB 16100
